        <p>When you setup a Module and configure the route (See Example)</p>

<h1>Example</h1>

<p>'manage' =&gt; array(
    'type'    =&gt; 'segment',
    'options' =&gt; array(
        'route'    =&gt; '/manage[/:action]',
        'constraints' =&gt; array(
            'action' =&gt; '[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_-]*',
        ),
        'defaults' =&gt; array(
            'controller' =&gt; 'Manage\Controller\Manage',
            'action'     =&gt; 'index',
        ),
    ),
),</p>

